thread.title: Ugandan shilling seen vulnerable to losses on high liquidity

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Ugandan shilling seen vulnerable to losses on high liquidity

organizations.name: calculated cross rates deposits deposits & forwards uganda equities

text:
KAMPALA, April 11 (Reuters) - The Ugandan shilling was stable on Wednesday but traders said it was vulnerable to depreciation on the back of importer demand and abundant local currency liquidity in the money markets.
